Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束在异世界 锡菲罗的痛苦战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 龙咲海 与狮堂光、凤凰寺风三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在充满回忆的东京塔 再度被召唤到锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得到锡菲罗的欧多札姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达 与法连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个国家也进攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个来路不明的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得到这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是迪波尼亚与
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得跟小光一模一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做新星的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗城短暂的和平 很快就被结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星出现在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星对小光放话说 要杀死兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第41话 与新星的战斗及魔物的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大姐姐是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道新星到哪里去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用最痛苦 最难受的方法杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与小光的波动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物又出现在居住区了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气是…小光？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小光吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在指示我 兰迪斯的位置吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问你有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是 你干嘛担心我这个敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光喜欢的人我全都讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把这种人杀光光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么长得跟小光一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我就是小光呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小光创造我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光也不讨厌你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我讨厌你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然接二连三地出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔兽召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是导师古列夫告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉法格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你只属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠的鼓动在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙到底是 怎样进入城内的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从那个黑洞中出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得比刚才还要强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 比刚才更强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧创造了魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗是意志的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物也是心所创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些魔物是我们的心创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从刚才看到现在 终于搞懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个球体会吸收恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那力量创造魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可以害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会产生出更可怕的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心痛了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么避不开呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的喜欢兰迪斯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死兰迪斯的大哥的小光呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他不会喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还要喜欢上他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐们不会说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 大姐姐 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是恐惧在创造魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物的力量减弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么相信之心 可恶的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧 新星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后有的是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要听话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会令你属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 新星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的魔物是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们精神变好以后 魔物就突然变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果然是心所创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧心会创造魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕的心 会使魔物变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们是在跟自己的心作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死兰迪斯的大哥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知他不会喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何还要喜欢上他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:24.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如吹越广大海洋的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:32.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦放出数不清的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:39.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,执意隐藏起受伤的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:43.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,迎向明天的白色背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:47.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,令我再也看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:51.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,让我轻轻地抹掉你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:54.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,让我轻轻地拥抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:23:02.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的胸中获得安憩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:06.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you I'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:17.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,歇起翅膀 梦还是不会结束
